{"tid":578861,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"（5月9/10/11尋人）峴港包車一日遊美山聖地同會安","createTime":"2018-03-03T04:51:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T05:29:15.000Z","uid":88651,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f56ff6eaf7e98fce3c1109ac3dfc537a3071f780","tid":578861,"uid":88651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T04:51:42.000Z","msg":"我打算5月9-11 是但一日中午去美山聖地 然後再去會安<br />\n上網睇4人包車個價大約係$700（9小時）<br />\n有無巴絲果幾日會人在峴港又想去美山同會安？<br />\n我同朋友兩個人，如果搵到多一個或兩個除番開平少少都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到時岩玩可以一齊玩，想有私人時間唔一齊玩純粹夾份包車都得<br />\n<br />\n請留tg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f535fef4f3494b3a180640f1d7ed2aefedc2b04","tid":578861,"uid":88651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T05:08:19.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自問我同友人都幾玩得 易相處<br />\n上年同樣時間去左西藏<br />\n有無人呢段時間都想去峴港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f372fd7b6bbc0964a4f7a0aee65c6ea22f3867ea","tid":578861,"uid":18825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T13:26:32.000Z","msg":"有興趣<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joejoecho\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoejoecho&d=dNRlovAxmi7Kun9qqq6%2FDr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=34bdf7bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joejoecho</a>"},{"pid":"ce4d205c03a1263cfff569db8fdd76427e2aee73","tid":578861,"uid":88651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f372fd7b6bbc0964a4f7a0aee65c6ea22f3867ea","tid":578861,"uid":18825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T13:26:32.000Z","msg":"有興趣<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joejoecho\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoejoecho&d=dNRlovAxmi7Kun9qqq6%2FDr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=34bdf7bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joejoecho</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T15:21:46.000Z","msg":"已加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n由於唔打算係會安住一晚<br />\n想一日內峴港去美山 美山去會安 會安再番峴港<br />\n所以唯一辦法係要包車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無巴絲同期又想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b8914e8ae4d40b7260ef99e4e176a48dab3afa5","tid":578861,"uid":61903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T17:29:35.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲宜家係峴港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解咁多人話去食海鮮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正常價正常味道咋嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋夜晚係咪冇野玩"},{"pid":"bbf9eeae105c25d6b79d78d1e54c0a6449b2119c","tid":578861,"uid":88651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b8914e8ae4d40b7260ef99e4e176a48dab3afa5","tid":578861,"uid":61903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T17:29:35.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲宜家係峴港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解咁多人話去食海鮮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正常價正常味道咋嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋夜晚係咪冇野玩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T17:53:32.000Z","msg":"我都想知<br />\n上網見好多人話要食Quan Be Man<br />\n是咪真係又抵又好食"},{"pid":"a33f9ff7121319c0763de2e0310fda3709a5cf36","tid":578861,"uid":61903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbf9eeae105c25d6b79d78d1e54c0a6449b2119c","tid":578861,"uid":88651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b8914e8ae4d40b7260ef99e4e176a48dab3afa5","tid":578861,"uid":61903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T17:29:35.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲宜家係峴港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解咁多人話去食海鮮<img 